        public double estimateDistance(Vector p,
                               Vector q)
        Description copied from interface: Heuristic
        Estimates the distance between two points p, q without considering the map or obstacles between p and q by a heuristic. A valid implementation fulfills following properties: (p,q) >= 0, (p,p) = 0 (p,q) == (q,p) (p,z) + (z,q) <= (p,q)
        Specified by:
        estimateDistance in interface Heuristic
        Returns:
        Estimated distance of p and q without considering the map or obstacles between p and q.
